1c:T41a,Internal evidence clearly describes a 7% didecyldimethyl ammonium chloride (DDAC) surface disinfectant under the 'Inviro' brand name by Meril Life Sciences. The product is a 4th generation QAC formulation for healthcare surface disinfection. However, external evidence references 'Envirocide' (a different product with similar use case) rather than 'Inviro,' creating ambiguity about product verification. The manufacturer source (tier1) confirms Meril's 360 Infection Prevention division exists and produces disinfectants, supporting the internal evidence. No direct external validation of 'Inviro' brand name was found - only similar competing products. The brand is missing from internal data but appears in product name. Classification as quaternary ammonium compound surface disinfectant is consistent and verifiable. Recommend manual review to: (1) confirm 'Inviro' brand name authenticity, (2) obtain manufacturer product literature, (3) verify this is not a catalog naming error for another product like Envirocide or a private-label version.18:["$","$L1b",null,{"product":{"product_name":"Inviro Surface Cleaner/Disinfectant","product_name_display":"Inviro Surface Cleaner/Disinfectant","sku_code":"MRL-INF-004","product_family":"Inviro Surface Cleaner/Disinfectant","product_family_display":"Inviro Surface Cleaner/Disinfectant","slug":"inviro-surface-cleaner-disinfectant","images":[{"id":"86acf0b61edc","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c17bd504841ec9248cfade/cover_2f78c6f5.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Surgical Gowns Brochure 27-09-2025.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":262286,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:58:30.484849+00:00","source":"division_fallback","width":1654,"height":2339}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"Inviro Surface Cleaner/Disinfectant | Inviro Surface Disinfectants - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"Inviro Surface Cleaner/Disinfectant features 7% didecyldimethyl ammonium chlorid